articles.title: Bird was entangled in Verstappen's F1 car for Canadian GP - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Red Bull has revealed that the remains of the bird that Max Verstappen hit in the Canadian Grand Prix got entangled in his car for the entire Formula 1 race.
articles.content:
Verstappen radioed his team on lap 11 of the Montreal event to notify the pit wall that he had struck a bird on the exit of one of the corners.
